Josiane Balasko https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Josiane_Balasko 0 Josiane Balasko (born Josiane Balašković; 15 April 1950) is a French actress, writer and director. She has been nominated seven times for César Awards, and won twice. Josiane_Balasko ( born Josiane_Balašković ; 15_April_1950 ) is a_French_actress_,_writer_and_director .
